# ── Live Google reviews (Featurable) ───────────────────────────────────────────
# The "Was unsere Kunden über ihre Projekte sagen" section pulls live Google
# reviews from a free Featurable widget. Without this set, the section renders a
# curated static fallback list (src/lib/reviews/fallback.ts).
#
# Setup:
#   1. Create a free account at https://featurable.com and connect the Google
#      Business Profile ("Fast Systemmöbel").
#   2. Create a widget at https://featurable.com/app/widgets.
#   3. Copy the widget ID and paste it below.
# The feed is filtered to recent 4–5★ reviews and refreshed every 6 hours (ISR).
FEATURABLE_WIDGET_ID=
